从官网下载https://docs.sonarqube.org/display/SCAN/Analyzing+with+SonarQube+Scanner
解压
创建测试目录test
创建程序目录python
#目录结构
-test
            -python/程序目录
            -sonar-project.properties
            
配置sonar-project.properties #python为例
sonar.projectKey=Python-Test1
sonar.projectName=Python-Test1
sonar.projectVersion=1.0
sonar.sources=python
sonar.language=py
sonar.sourceEncoding=UTF-8

将程序放入python目录下
再目录test下，使用绝对路径执行/opt/sonar/sonarscan/sonar-scanner-3.3.0.1492/bin/sonar-scanner
